<body>
<Nav />
<main id="main-content">
  <section class="hero bg-grid" aria-label="Elevar pricing 2026">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <nav aria-label="Breadcrumb" style="margin-bottom:16px;">
        <ol style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;color:var(--text-4);">
          <li><a href="https://stackarchitect.xyz/" style="color:var(--text-4);text-decoration:none;">Home</a></li>
          <li aria-hidden="true" style="color:var(--border);">/</li>
          <li style="color:var(--text-3);">Elevar Pricing 2026</li>
        </ol>
      </nav>
      <div class="hero-dateline">Updated April 2026 · Elevar pricing analysis · Shopify</div>
      <div style="background:rgba(0,200,100,.06);border-left:3px solid var(--g);padding:14px 20px;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;margin-bottom:24px;max-width:680px;">
        <p style="font-size:15px;font-weight:500;color:var(--text);margin:0;line-height:1.65;"><strong style="color:var(--g);">Direct answer:</strong> Elevar costs $0 (browser only), $50/mo (Starter — Meta + Google CAPI), $250/mo (Growth — adds TikTok/Pinterest/Consent Mode), or $500/mo (Pro — full managed stack). Server-side tracking starts at $50/month.</p>
      </div>
      <h1>Elevar Pricing 2026 —<br><span class="green">Every Plan</span><br><span class="dim">Broken Down Honestly.</span></h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">Elevar has four pricing tiers. Most Shopify stores need exactly one feature — server-side tracking — which starts at $50/month. This guide breaks down what each plan actually includes, who needs it, and whether the cost is justified for your store size and ad spend.</p>
      <div class="cost-row">
        <div class="cost-pill"><div class="cost-v" style="color:var(--g);">$0/mo</div><div class="cost-l">Free tier</div></div>
        <div class="cost-pill"><div class="cost-v">$50/mo</div><div class="cost-l">Starter (CAPI)</div></div>
        <div class="cost-pill"><div class="cost-v" style="color:var(--amber);">$250/mo</div><div class="cost-l">Growth</div></div>
        <div class="cost-pill"><div class="cost-v" style="color:var(--red);">$500/mo</div><div class="cost-l">Pro</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-ctas">
        <a href="#tiers" class="btn-outline" onclick="event.preventDefault();document.getElementById('tiers').scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth'})">See All Tiers <svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg></a>
        <a href="#verdict" class="btn pulse" onclick="event.preventDefault();document.getElementById('verdict').scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth'})">Is It Worth It? <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"></path></svg></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PRICING TIERS -->
