          <ul style="list-style:none;padding:0;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:7px;">
            <li style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-3);display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:baseline;"><span style="color:var(--g);flex-shrink:0;">✓</span>Meta Conversions API (server-side)</li>
            <li style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-3);display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:baseline;"><span style="color:var(--g);flex-shrink:0;">✓</span>Google Enhanced Conversions</li>
            <li style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-3);display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:baseline;"><span style="color:var(--g);flex-shrink:0;">✓</span>Event deduplication</li>
            <li style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-3);display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:baseline;"><span style="color:var(--g);flex-shrink:0;">✓</span>First-party data layer</li>
            <li style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-3);display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:baseline;"><span style="color:var(--red);flex-shrink:0;">✗</span><span>No TikTok/Pinterest/Snapchat CAPI</span></li>
            <li style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-3);display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:baseline;"><span style="color:var(--red);flex-shrink:0;">✗</span><span>No Consent Mode v2</span></li>
          </ul>
          <div style="margin-top:16px;padding:8px 12px;background:rgba(0,200,100,.08);border-radius:6px;font-size:11px;color:var(--g);font-weight:500;">iOS-proof Meta + Google. Recovers 20–40% of lost conversions.</div>
        </div>
        <!-- Growth -->
        <div style="border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;padding:22px;background:var(--bg);">
          <div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;font-weight:700;color:var(--amber);letter-spacing:.12em;margin-bottom:10px;">GROWTH</div>
          <div style="font-size:28px;font-weight:900;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:2px;">$250</div>
          <div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text-4);margin-bottom:16px;">per month</div>
          <ul style="list-style:none;padding:0;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:7px;">
            <li style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-3);display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:baseline;"><span style="color:var(--g);flex-shrink:0;">✓</span>Everything in Starter</li>
            <li style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-3);display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:baseline;"><span style="color:var(--g);flex-shrink:0;">✓</span>TikTok Events API</li>
            <li style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-3);display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:baseline;"><span style="color:var(--g);flex-shrink:0;">✓</span>Pinterest CAPI</li>
            <li style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-3);display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:baseline;"><span style="color:var(--g);flex-shrink:0;">✓</span>Snapchat CAPI</li>
            <li style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-3);display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:baseline;"><span style="color:var(--g);flex-shrink:0;">✓</span>Google Consent Mode v2</li>
            <li style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-3);display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:baseline;"><span style="color:var(--g);flex-shrink:0;">✓</span>Behavioural modelling (GDPR)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <!-- Pro -->
        <div style="border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;padding:22px;background:var(--bg);">
          <div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;font-weight:700;color:var(--red);letter-spacing:.12em;margin-bottom:10px;">PRO</div>
          <div style="font-size:28px;font-weight:900;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:2px;">$500</div>
          <div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text-4);margin-bottom:16px;">per month</div>
          <ul style="list-style:none;padding:0;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:7px;">
            <li style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-3);display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:baseline;"><span style="color:var(--g);flex-shrink:0;">✓</span>Everything in Growth</li>
            <li style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-3);display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:baseline;"><span style="color:var(--g);flex-shrink:0;">✓</span>Fully managed data layer</li>
            <li style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-3);display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:baseline;"><span style="color:var(--g);flex-shrink:0;">✓</span>Custom event schemas</li>
            <li style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-3);display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:baseline;"><span style="color:var(--g);flex-shrink:0;">✓</span>Priority support</li>
            <li style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-3);display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:baseline;"><span style="color:var(--g);flex-shrink:0;">✓</span>Dedicated implementation help</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Annual cost table -->
      <div style="border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:32px;">
        <div style="background:var(--bg-3);padding:12px 18px;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;font-weight:700;color:var(--text-4);letter-spacing:.12em;">// ANNUAL COST REALITY CHECK</div>
        <table style="width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:13px;">
          <thead><tr style="border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);"><th style="padding:11px 18px;text-align:left;color:var(--text-4);font-weight:500;">Plan</th><th style="padding:11px 18px;text-align:right;color:var(--text-4);font-weight:500;">Monthly</th><th style="padding:11px 18px;text-align:right;color:var(--text-4);font-weight:500;">Annual cost</th><th style="padding:11px 18px;text-align:left;color:var(--text-4);font-weight:500;">Server-side CAPI?</th></tr></thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);"><td style="padding:11px 18px;color:var(--text-3);">Free</td><td style="padding:11px 18px;text-align:right;color:var(--g);font-weight:600;">$0</td><td style="padding:11px 18px;text-align:right;color:var(--g);">$0</td><td style="padding:11px 18px;color:var(--red);">No</td></tr>
            <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);background:rgba(0,200,100,.03);"><td style="padding:11px 18px;color:var(--text);font-weight:600;">Starter</td><td style="padding:11px 18px;text-align:right;color:var(--text-3);">$50</td><td style="padding:11px 18px;text-align:right;color:var(--text-3);">$600/yr</td><td style="padding:11px 18px;color:var(--g);">Yes — Meta + Google</td></tr>
            <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);"><td style="padding:11px 18px;color:var(--text-3);">Growth</td><td style="padding:11px 18px;text-align:right;color:var(--amber);">$250</td><td style="padding:11px 18px;text-align:right;color:var(--amber);">$3,000/yr</td><td style="padding:11px 18px;color:var(--g);">Yes — Meta, Google, TikTok, Pinterest, Snapchat</td></tr>
            <tr><td style="padding:11px 18px;color:var(--text-3);">Pro</td><td style="padding:11px 18px;text-align:right;color:var(--red);">$500</td><td style="padding:11px 18px;text-align:right;color:var(--red);">$6,000/yr</td><td style="padding:11px 18px;color:var(--g);">Yes — everything + managed layer</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- IS IT WORTH IT VERDICT -->
  <section class="section" id="verdict">
    <div class="inner-md">
      <div class="sec-head">
        <span class="tag tag-dim" style="margin-bottom:14px;display:inline-flex;">// Honest verdict</span>
        <h2>Is Elevar worth the cost for your store?</h2>
        <p>The answer depends entirely on what you need it to do.</p>
      </div>

      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:16px;margin-bottom:32px;">
        <div style="border:1px solid rgba(0,200,100,.2);border-radius:10px;padding:22px;background:rgba(0,200,100,.03);">
          <div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;font-weight:700;color:var(--g);letter-spacing:.12em;margin-bottom:14px;">✓ ELEVAR IS WORTH IT IF...</div>
          <ul style="list-style:none;padding:0;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;">
            <li style="font-size:14px;color:var(--text-3);line-height:1.65;">You spend <strong style="color:var(--text);">$5,000+/month on Meta Ads</strong> and need the most robust server-side setup with dedicated support</li>
            <li style="font-size:14px;color:var(--text-3);line-height:1.65;">You operate in <strong style="color:var(--text);">GDPR markets</strong> and need Google Consent Mode v2 with behavioural modelling (Growth+ only)</li>
            <li style="font-size:14px;color:var(--text-3);line-height:1.65;">You run <strong style="color:var(--text);">Pinterest or Snapchat Ads</strong> and need server-side coverage for those platforms too (Growth+)</li>
            <li style="font-size:14px;color:var(--text-3);line-height:1.65;">You want a <strong style="color:var(--text);">fully managed solution</strong> with no technical setup or maintenance responsibility</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div style="border:1px solid rgba(239,68,68,.2);border-radius:10px;padding:22px;background:rgba(239,68,68,.03);">
          <div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;font-weight:700;color:var(--red);letter-spacing:.12em;margin-bottom:14px;">✗ ELEVAR IS NOT WORTH IT IF...</div>
          <ul style="list-style:none;padding:0;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;">
            <li style="font-size:14px;color:var(--text-3);line-height:1.65;">Your primary need is <strong style="color:var(--text);">server-side Meta + Google tracking only</strong> — CAPI Shield delivers this at $0</li>
            <li style="font-size:14px;color:var(--text-3);line-height:1.65;">You are comfortable <strong style="color:var(--text);">running a Make.com scenario</strong> — a one-time 6-minute setup</li>
            <li style="font-size:14px;color:var(--text-3);line-height:1.65;">You spend <strong style="color:var(--text);">less than $2,000/month on ads</strong> — $50–$600/year is a high overhead at that scale</li>
            <li style="font-size:14px;color:var(--text-3);line-height:1.65;">You only need <strong style="color:var(--text);">Meta and Google CAPI</strong> — that is exactly what the free stack covers</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div style="border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;background:var(--bg-3);padding:24px 28px;">
        <div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;font-weight:700;color:var(--text-4);letter-spacing:.12em;margin-bottom:12px;">// THE HONEST SUMMARY</div>
        <p style="font-size:15px;color:var(--text-3);line-height:1.8;margin:0;">Elevar's Starter plan at $50/month is legitimate value if you want a managed server-side tracking setup with no technical overhead. The same technical outcome — Meta CAPI + Google Enhanced Conversions — is achievable free via <a href="/capi-shield" style="color:var(--g);">CAPI Shield</a>. The $50 is paying for the managed interface and the Elevar data layer, not for access to the APIs themselves. At Growth ($250/month) and Pro ($500/month), the additional platforms and consent mode integration justify the cost for the stores that genuinely use those features. For most Shopify stores spending under $10,000/month on ads running Meta and Google only, the free alternative is functionally equivalent.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
